---
title: Maple Magic Pork Chops with Broccoli, Pecans, and a Double Potato Mash
description: It’s hard to resist the sweet, sweet magic of maple syrup. But is there anywhere that it works besides pancakes and waffles? The answer to that question is yes—this recipe proves that it’s just as amazing with pork and a couple of complementary sides. Here, pan-seared chops are drizzled with a maple pan sauce, making for one truly delicious sweet and savory combination that only gets better with the addition of mashed potatoes, broccoli, and a pecan garnish.
